So what we are going to talk about, and what you are going to listen to, and what you are

01:10.640 --> 01:17.000
going to take part in in the next ten weeks, is much more important than just a learning

01:17.000 --> 01:18.000
experience.

01:18.000 --> 01:21.120
It is a creative experience.

01:21.120 --> 01:24.280
You are creating your future.

01:24.280 --> 01:30.400
There is nothing more important because in your future lies the history and the future

01:30.400 --> 01:32.480
of the human species.

01:32.480 --> 01:39.200
The ISU class of 88 is going to be a major component in the space leadership of the world

01:39.200 --> 01:40.200
in the future.

01:40.200 --> 01:46.160
These are impressive young professionals with a formidable list of credentials to their

01:46.160 --> 01:47.160
credit.

01:47.160 --> 01:53.680
