06:45.160 --> 06:50.760
century, with students and faculty actually studying and working in space.

06:50.760 --> 06:56.440
I think the ISU concept as well as other concepts like this is an absolute seedbed to spring

06:56.440 --> 06:59.600
new ideas and innovation into our total process.

06:59.600 --> 07:03.560
The ISU is building international bridges.

07:03.560 --> 07:07.080
To move out into space is going to be very, very expensive, and I think if we're going

07:07.080 --> 07:11.000
